name: My Little Undulant #1
description:
Your Undulant is personalised to you. Its movement is tied to your Wallet ID and its Objkt ID.
If you are unsynced you will see a generic seed. Sync your wallet to see your own version.

The colour set is also tied to your Wallet ID and the Objkt ID and the Undulant will return to its colour set every reload.
However, you can cycle colour sets using the ‘c’ and ‘x’ keys.
